Package: ggfittext
Title: Fit Text Inside a Box
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Wilkins", email = "david@wilkox.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2 geoms to fit text into a box by growing, shrinking
    or wrapping the text.
